==Russian==
===Conjunction===
'''чтоб''' (štob) ''(+ past tense or the infinitive)''

# that...should ''(subjunctive)''
# so that, in order that
#:*{{RUchar|Невозмо́жно, чтоб она́ э́то сде́лала}} — ''It’s impossible that she should have done this; She could not possibly have done this.''
# [[lest]]
#:*{{RUchar|чтоб я не забы́л}} — ''lest I forget; so that I won’t forget.''

